data.description: Take a look at this newly painted 2 story home located on a large corner lot with easy access to Loop 410, and walking distance to shopping centers! This 3 bedroom 1.5 bath home has so much potential, just needs your own personal touch to make it your home. New HVAC system and electrical replaced throughout the entire home, updated bathroom, granite kitchen countertops, and a backyard with endless possibilities!
